<div class="fy_zcbj">

    <div class="fy_sqw">
    	<h3>【置顶】妇科学科带头人招聘公告</h3>
      <i>发布时间：2026-01-30 08:31   来源：   浏览次数：<script type='text/javascript' src='/web/news_checknum.rt?contentId=15721&channlId=15'></script></i>
       
        <div style="color:#000000;">
      		<p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center;line-height:37px"><br/></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">陕西省中医药研究院（省中医医院</span> <span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">省中西医结合研究所）是陕西省</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">人民</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">政府举办的一所综合性科研、医疗、教学中医机构。先后入选国家中医药传承创新工程、国家区域医疗中心输出医院，获批国家中医紧急医学救援基地、国家中医康复中心，纳入国家中医药传承创新中心项目储备库，并正在申报国家医学中心（中医类）。</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">为加强我院妇科学科建设，提升临床诊疗与科研水平，现面向全社会公开招聘妇科学科带头人。我们诚挚邀请德才兼备、富有创新精神的妇科领域专家加入，共同推动学科高质量发展。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">一、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">招聘岗位</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">妇科学科带头人</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">1名</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">二、岗位职责</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">1.</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">全面负责妇科临床、教学、科研及管理工作，制定学科发展规划并组织实施；</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">2.</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">引领专科技术发展，开展新技术、新项目，提升</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">科室诊疗水平与学术影响力</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">；</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">3.</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">强化学科人才梯队建设，培养骨干力量，打造高水平团队；</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">4.</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">推动科研创新，牵头国家级、省部级科研项目，产出高水平成果；</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">5.</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">促进学术交流，扩大科室在国内外影响力。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">三、任职要求</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">1.具有中华人民共和国国籍，拥护中国共产党的领导，遵纪守法，品行端正，热爱医疗卫生事业</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">，具</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">有良好的团队合作</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">精神</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">、职业道德追求和奉献精神</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">；</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">身心健康，能正常履职；自觉遵守国家</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">法律法规</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">，无</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">违法犯罪行为</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">记录；</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">2.原则上不超过50周岁；</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">3.</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">具有博士研究生学历学位</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">，主任医师</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">职称；</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">4</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">.有10年及以上国内三甲医院工作经验，</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">具备科室管理经验，</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">具有较高的学术影响力及业内同行认可的专业特长，所在学科（专科）发展优势显著</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">；</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">5.特别优秀者年龄、学历可适当放宽。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">四、薪酬待遇</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">薪酬面议，待遇从优，</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">具体待遇</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">“一人一策”按照合同执行。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">五、应聘方式</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">需提供以下应聘材料：</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">1.</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">个人简历；</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">2.</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">身份证、各阶段学历学位证、资格证、执业证、职称证、学会任职、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">获奖证书；近</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">5年代表性</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">科研</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">成果</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">（论文、科研项目</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">著作、专利</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">等</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">）</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">；学会任职、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">人才称号、获奖证书</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">；（扫描件合并至一个</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">PDF）</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">3.学科建设与发展规划设想。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">请将</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">应聘材料</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">发送至邮箱：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">sxszyyy@163.com，邮件标题格式：“</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">妇科学科带头人应聘</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">＋姓名</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">”。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">六、联系方式</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">1.联 系 人：由</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">老师</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">029-87252512</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">2.联系邮箱：sxszyyy@163.com</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">3.联系地址：陕西省西安市莲湖区西华门4号</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">我们期待与您携手，共创妇科发展的崭新篇章！</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px; text-align: right; line-height: 37px;"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">陕西省中医药研究院</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:right;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">（省中医医院</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">省中西医结合研究所）</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px; text-align: right; line-height: 37px;"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">组织人事处</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 299px; line-height: 37px; text-align: right;"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">2026年1月29日</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>
      	</div>
    </div>


</div>


